snippet.title: Million Depth - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2555950/Million_Depth/

In this deep-diving action strategy game, Moma, a girl who was left all alone in outer space, visits Earth and dives into the million-floor deep underground world in search of her only friend, ""You"".
